title: Casual Club Looking For Some Sydney Members
body:
Hey, I've created a club for Sydney players if anyone's keen.

A good place to find other players to play Ranked/Norms/Aram

replies.body:
Hey Mate1

I wanna join in your club!

See ya

Cool ! I can play once a fortnight I'm level 17. What did you have in mind ?
I just played my 2nd normal it was fun ! The first time I tried at lvl 3 i got flame flame so I waited til now.  
I played Aram twice loved it too !
